Package com.soa.auth.credential

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryTokenCredential
    This class represents an arbitrary customized credential objects that can be put into a Subject's public credential set.
    CookieCredential  
    DomainListCredential
    This represents a list of domains that a user wants to authenticate against.
    NameCredential
    This represents name credential.
    PasswordCredential
    This represents a username/password credential.
    SSOTokenCredential
    An object to hold the SSO Token name and value when it is contained in the list of credentials within a Subject;
